title: Football: Depth chart confirms open competition at kicker
text:
Football: Depth chart confirms open competition at kicker Football: Depth chart confirms open competition at kicker By Bobby La Gesse rlagesse@amestrib.com 
Iowa State football coach Paul Rhoads indicated an open kicker competition was coming. The depth chart for the TCU game, released on Monday, confirmed it. 
Kicker was listed as Cole Netten or Chris Francis. Netten, a junior, has struggled in 2015. Heâ€™s 7 of 12 on field goals and missed a 40-yard kick against Texas Tech last week.
